messages.message:
Here are the limitations on the split-classification internal release (not yet in the linked internal release notes):
• Split classification projects can not be moved across workspaces
• Split-classification does not work on files digitized with form recognizer
• Provenance doesn’t work when doing extraction on split records that are long docs and are not the first record in the file
cc @Tom @Lee
And we are working on addressing these limited in 24.02
